[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "最後まで残っていた者が勝ちの武道会、か。\n獣人限定ならば、参加できるのは俺とイザナと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00936",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "僕もやるよ！　一緒に頑張ろうね、兄さん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00937",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "最後にティムと俺が残ったら、俺は即降参する",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00938",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "あんまり露骨だと、\n観客のみんなががっかりしちゃわないかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00939",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ティム。お前はなんて優しいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00940",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ランターナ王国騎士団の強さをお披露目する機会！\nハンマーを磨いて準備しないと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00941",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ふふっ、イザナちゃん張り切ってるなぁ。\n私たちも何か力になれないかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00942",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "武道会の規定を読んだんだけど、\n武器とか道具を使ってもいいみたいなんだよねえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00943",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あの国王らしい豪快な取り決めっすわ。\nわりとなんでもありだと思っていい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00944",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "道具がありなら、疲れたとき用に\n体力を回復できるものを用意しておこうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00945",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "おお、いいんじゃない？　というか調合した道具を\nごっそり持ち込めば楽に勝てるやも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00946",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あはは……でも、裏を返せば相手も道具を使えるって\nことだし、油断はできなさそう。ひとまず回復かぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00947",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "片手で簡単に食べられて、栄養豊富な携帯食料……\nちょっと考えてみようかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00948",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "鍛冶屋でハンマーを鍛える道具も買ったし、\nあとは……クンクン",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00949",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ふわぁ、甘くて美味しそうな匂い……\n腹ごしらえも必要だね。腹が減ってはなんとやら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00950",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アイス売りの女",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そこのかわいいお嬢ちゃん。どうだい？\nとっても甘いはちみつアイス、試食してみないかい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_709_036_00951",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ほんと！？　ありがとう！\nいただきまーす！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00952",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "……あまーい！　でも、甘いだけじゃない？\nちょっと苦いのがあって、でもそれが甘さを……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00953",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "これ……ヤバ、なんか、きゅうに、ねむ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00954",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アイス売りの女",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おや、大丈夫かい？　熱中症かねえ。\nほら、うちで休んでおいき……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_709_036_00955",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "くっ……！　だいじょ、ぶ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00956",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、イザナちゃ――どうしたの！？　大丈夫！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00957",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アイス売りの女",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……チッ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_709_036_00958",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……ってことがあったんです。\n幸いイザナちゃんは無事でしたけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00959",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ごめん、アタシとしたことが浮かれてた……\nあのアイスに、なんか入ってたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00960",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "私たちが聞き込みに行っている間に\nそんなことになってたなんて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00961",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そのアイス売りの女、クロだな。\n誘拐の実行犯だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00962",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "今すぐ逮捕しに行きましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00963",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや、もう遅い。手口が割れた以上\n相手は二度と同じ手は使わんだろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00964",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "こっちは武道会で勝ち抜かなきゃいけないのに\n行方不明事件も続いてるんじゃ困っちゃうわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00965",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "こちらも王宮に捜査の協力を要求したんですけど\nなんだかあんまり反応が良くなくて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00966",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "王のように欲しければ力で奪い取れというお国柄か、\nあるいは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00967",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "とにかく王宮の支援が期待できない分、\n私がいつもの３倍頑張ります！　むんっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00968",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それじゃあ、私たちは引き続き聞き込みってことね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00969",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい！　イザナさんの件も気になりますし、\n行方不明事件、テキパキ解決しましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00970",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]